title: Armed robbery of supermarket at Eight Mile Plains | The
text:
The man entered the supermarket on Holmead Rd, Eight Mile Plains, about 3pm armed with a gun and making demands for cash.
A female attendant did not comply with his demands and he fled the store with food and cigarettes.
No one was injured during the incident.
Police have released a CCTV image of the suspect. He is described as 180-185cm tall, with slim build and olive complexion.
Police are also investigating the armed robbery of a grocery store in Holland Park this evening.
About 6.20pm a man armed with a handgun entered the Seville Rd business and demanded cash.
The male attendant complied with his demands and the man fled on foot the cash.
No one was injured during the incident.
The man is described as approximately 185cm tall with a slim build.
He was last seen wearing black trousers, black shoes, blue flannelette jacket over a grey hooded shirt, and white gloves
Anyone with information to contact Crime Stoppers on 1800 333 000 or crimestoppers.com.au .
